1
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:13,340
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:16,660
Episode 53

3
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:23,460
Well,

4
00:02:24,940 --> 00:02:26,260
do these spiritual birds

5
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,420
fly here to dance every year?

6
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:34,420
Do you think they've got nothing else to do?

7
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:38,020
So you summoned them specially?

8
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:38,740
Well,

9
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:39,700
well,

10
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,660
just ask them to come closer.

11
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:43,740
Ask them to do the dance of
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix" for me closer.

12
00:02:50,940 --> 00:02:53,340
I won't do it for nothing.

13
00:02:54,380 --> 00:02:55,580
How will you return the favor?

14
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:58,860
Don't be so stingy.

15
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:01,460
I've taught you how to make the sweet and sour fish.

16
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,660
Or do you want to watch me dance?

17
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:07,980
I'm quite a good dancer,

18
00:03:08,260 --> 00:03:09,180
far better than

19
00:03:09,180 --> 00:03:10,580
your foster sister Zhihe.

20
00:03:11,220 --> 00:03:13,260
I just can't dance for others.

21
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:16,580
Just make them do the dance of

22
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:17,340
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix" for me.

23
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:17,980
Never in my life

24
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:18,780
have I watched real birds

25
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:20,780
do the dance of "Paying Homage to the Phoenix".

26
00:03:21,140 --> 00:03:22,180
If you ask them to dance for me,

27
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,580
I'll dance for you.

28
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:24,860
Xiaobai,

29
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:28,180
in front of others,

30
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,380
you're always polite and well-behaved,

31
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:32,260
pretending to be elegant and experienced,

32
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,100
but I know that you're just

33
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,020
a mischievous and spoiled girl.

34
00:03:36,940 --> 00:03:39,900
You used to restrain yourself in front of me,

35
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,380
for example, in the Fanyin Valley

36
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,700
and in the Dream of Aranya.

37
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:47,140
Compared to the previous girl
who was restrained in front of me,

38
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:49,500
I like the present girl more,

39
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:51,380
who is innocent and spoiled.

40
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,860
This is the real you.

41
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:55,540
Miao Luo once said that

42
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:56,940
there was a sea of Foling flowers in my heart.

43
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:59,740
She wondered who was hidden behind the flowers.

44
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:01,140
Xiaobai,

45
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:03,900
I know that there has always been

46
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:06,420
a little red fox hiding behind the flowers.

47
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:09,660
Though I was not in love with you back then,

48
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:13,140
I've always treated you differently.

49
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:15,660
Just make them dance for me.

50
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:16,900
Don't ignore me.

51
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:18,940
It's a real bargain!

52
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,780
It really is!

53
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:29,340
Then you should dance for me first.

54
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:31,100
Well,

55
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:33,780
we'd better not keep
the spiritual birds waiting for too long.

56
00:04:34,140 --> 00:04:36,020
Can you ask them to dance for me first?

57
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:37,380
I'll dance for you later.

58
00:04:37,860 --> 00:04:39,180
As a majestic god,

59
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,900
you should show compassion.

60
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:44,860
I'm just afraid that someone might act in a slick way.

61
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,660
Didn't you say

62
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:50,020
you really wanted to return the favor?

63
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:52,740
Now you're bargaining with me.

64
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:57,340
Where's your sincerity?

65
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,820
Since there's no music,

66
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,420
I can only do one part of the dance.

67
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:11,100
Now that you're dancing,

68
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,380
you should do the whole dance at least.

69
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:16,980
I'll play the music for you.

70
00:05:22,460 --> 00:05:24,300
You actually know how to play Konghou!

71
00:05:25,060 --> 00:05:27,020
I didn't know that.

72
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:28,380
I didn't play much.

73
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:30,620
Of course you didn't know.

74
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:35,580
Do you find your husband talented?

75
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:36,940
Hu...

76
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:37,660
Hus...

77
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,100
Husband.

78
00:05:39,780 --> 00:05:42,580
It's weird to hear you say that.

79
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:45,020
No!

80
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:47,420
The word "husband" is weird itself.

81
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:49,300
I'd better keep calling you "Your Majesty".

82
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,540
Come here.

83
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,180
What did you just call me?

84
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:04,260
Think it clearly.

85
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:07,180
I called you "Your Majesty".

86
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:08,300
Who am I to you?

87
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:12,780
Husband! You're my husband!

88
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,300
That's more like it.

89
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:18,620
Dance for me over there.

90
00:06:25,500 --> 00:06:27,260
You said you wanted to dance for me,

91
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:30,220
but you haven't started yet.

92
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,940
Don't you find yourself hard to deal with?

93
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:36,660
You're the one who's been messing with me!

94
00:06:55,620 --> 00:06:56,420
Xiaobai,

95
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,940
I've always known that you're pretty,

96
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:02,500
but you're not the enchanting type

97
00:07:03,540 --> 00:07:06,340
for you often bear an innocent and bright look.

98
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:09,420
How ridiculous I am! Only till now

99
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:12,060
do I realize that this innocent face

100
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:15,460
is actually coquettish.

101
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:19,500
Look at those gentle and soft eyes!

102
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,900
Are you trying to seduce me?

103
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:41,580
Come to me.

104
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,380
One minute you asked me to come here,

105
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:45,660
and the next minute, you asked me to come to you.

106
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:47,140
You should come to me yourself.

107
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,860
Why do you bother me all the time?

108
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:51,780
Please come to me!

109
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:01,060
Then you can't pet me.

110
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:03,980
I won't.

111
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:06,340
Really?

112
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:08,100
Yes.

113
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:16,740
I...

114
00:08:17,380 --> 00:08:19,660
I still have to watch the dance of
"Paying Homage to the Phoenix".

115
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:22,500
What's the fun in that?

116
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:25,220
Just watch me instead.

117
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:50,100
As long as Dong Hua doesn't investigate himself,

118
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,700
no one else can see through

119
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:53,340
my hallucinating ward.

120
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:55,180
What if Emperor Dong Hua comes here?

121
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:59,060
Then let's do it on his wedding day.

122
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:01,620
Even if anything happens to the demons,

123
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:03,300
he won't be able to come.

124
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:05,500
Yes!

125
00:09:07,420 --> 00:09:08,860
Nie Chuyin,

126
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:12,540
I have limited patience.

127
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:15,100
If anything goes wrong again...

128
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:16,420
Your Majesty, do feel relieved.

129
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:20,020
If I can't get the blood tear this time,

130
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:21,940
I'll end my life myself.

131
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:28,500
Don't move!

132
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,460
Your body was just made.

133
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,180
You need rest.

134
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:39,620
It's time!

135
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,380
I thought the delayed wedding banquet

136
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:52,540
is just an ordinary banquet,

137
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,540
so I only have to dress formally.

138
00:09:54,900 --> 00:09:56,660
I didn't expect to dress so fancily.

139
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:02,220
It's just like a dream!

140
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:07,460
Xiaobai,

141
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:11,820
I'll have this dream with you forever.

142
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:19,900
Your Majesty! Your Highness!

143
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:24,700
I didn't mean to interrupt.

144
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,740
I really have something urgent to report.

145
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:27,660
Never mind.

146
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:30,500
What's up?

147
00:10:31,940 --> 00:10:33,660
Has anything gone wrong with Ye Qingti?

148
00:10:33,860 --> 00:10:35,300
Your Highness, please don't worry.

149
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:36,460
The time has come.

150
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:37,980
Ye Qingti is about to wake up.

151
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:40,140
It's time to transfer cultivation to him.

152
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:42,340
Really?

153
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,060
I just

154
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:45,780
confirmed that.

155
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:47,420
Wonderful!

156
00:10:48,420 --> 00:10:49,260
Your Highness, I know that

157
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,660
you've been worried about Ye Qingti all the time,

158
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,380
so I came here to inform you.

159
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:54,700
Thank you, Lord Xie.

160
00:10:55,020 --> 00:10:56,420
Your Highness, you're welcome.

161
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:58,660
The earlier Ye Qingti obtains cultivation,

162
00:10:58,980 --> 00:11:00,820
the earlier he can start cultivating.

163
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:01,940
Thus, he can wash away the mortal dust

164
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,780
in the Ninth Heaven Jade Pool

165
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:05,180
and become an immortal earlier in future.

166
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:08,300
Well then, I'll go right away.

167
00:11:12,180 --> 00:11:13,380
Transfer cultivation to him?

168
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,940
Are you going to do that yourself?

169
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:19,540
He died because of me.

170
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:21,980
I can at least do this for him.

171
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:24,140
No.

172
00:11:27,340 --> 00:11:29,300
Sorry for breaking into the hall without reporting.

173
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,700
I should go and do some repair work

174
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:32,860
on Ye Qingti's body
so as to reduce possible problems he might have

175
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:35,180
when he becomes an immortal in future.

176
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:37,940
Your Majesty! Your Highness!

177
00:11:38,180 --> 00:11:39,900
I'm leaving.

178
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:46,980
Ye Qingti saved my life.

179
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:48,780
If I don't transfer my cultivation to him,

180
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,900
who will?

181
00:11:51,740 --> 00:11:52,220
Xiaobai,

182
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,700
having given Ye Qingti an immortal body,

183
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:58,340
you've paid back his favor.

184
00:11:59,100 --> 00:12:01,220
But I've only paid back half of his favor.

185
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:09,780
Your Majesty,

186
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:12,660
are you so in love with me that

187
00:12:13,300 --> 00:12:15,820
you can't bear to hear that I'm going to

188
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,740
transfer my cultivation to another man?

189
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:22,460
You're just a little fox over thirty thousand years old.

190
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,140
You don't have much cultivation.

191
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:26,220
If you give away half of your cultivation,

192
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:28,540
how can you survive the test and become a superior goddess

193
00:12:29,220 --> 00:12:32,060
if I'm not by your side in the future?

194
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:35,940
So it's only because of my poor cultivation.

195
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:39,380
Moreover,

196
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:41,380
even if I have to go through the test
of becoming a superior goddess,

197
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:43,580
that'll be tens of thousands of years later.

198
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:44,900
You just said

199
00:12:45,060 --> 00:12:46,820
you wanted to be with me forever.

200
00:12:47,020 --> 00:12:49,580
How can you not be with me then?

201
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:52,860
Right.

202
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:56,100
I'll definitely be with you.

203
00:12:58,980 --> 00:12:59,860
Such being the case,

204
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:01,420
let me transfer

205
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,420
my cultivation to him.

206
00:13:05,380 --> 00:13:05,940
Your Majesty,

207
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:07,380
how can I let you

208
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:08,620
transfer your cultivation to him?

209
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,740
Everything you do is concerned with

210
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:11,900
the stability of the Four Seas and Eight Deserts.

211
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:14,420
You'll have to give away half of your cultivation,

212
00:13:15,020 --> 00:13:15,660
but I only have to give

213
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,420
a tiny bit of my cultivation.

214
00:13:17,820 --> 00:13:18,620
I won't be affected.

215
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:19,620
No! No!

216
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:20,740
Your Majesty,

217
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:22,460
I know you're saying this for my good,

218
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:24,660
but Ye Qingti saved my life.

219
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,580
Though I can't respond to his love,

220
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:28,180
I can definitely bring him back to life.

221
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:29,900
That's my promise to him.

222
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:33,220
If I let Your Majesty fulfill my duties

223
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:34,140
all the time,

224
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:35,780
how can my subjects

225
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:37,460
trust me in future?

226
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,100
Xiaobai...

227
00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:40,500
Your Majesty,

228
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:42,740
I'm the Monarch of Qingqiu.

229
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,940
I'm not a woman

230
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,780
who needs your protection all the time.

231
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:51,500
I know.

232
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:53,820
You've always been strong and independent.

233
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:57,460
I'm the one who can't live without you.

234
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:05,100
Then I'll go with you

235
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:07,500
after our wedding.

236
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:10,820
Let's go together then.

