00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:00,940
the wedding etiquette

283
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,580
is merely a formality.

284
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:03,500
His Majesty said

285
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:04,700
he wouldn't restrain me.

286
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:06,940
I can do whatever I like.

287
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:11,060
Did His Majesty really say so?

288
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,300
Of course!

289
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,380
He has kept his words.

290
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:19,940
However, even so,

291
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,460
the Sky Kingdom is not Qingqiu.

292
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:25,260
You should be prudent and self-restraint in future.

293
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,860
Don't be willful as you were in Qingqiu.

294
00:18:28,060 --> 00:18:28,980
Do you understand?

295
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:30,700
I see.

296
00:18:31,020 --> 00:18:32,900
If there's any rule I don't understand in the Sky Kingdom,

297
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,660
I'll consult Immortal Officials such as Chong Lin.

298
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:35,740
Father, do feel relieved.

299
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:38,580
Well. Father, I'm leaving.

300
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:39,940
Mother has got plenty of things

301
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:40,980
for me to handle.

302
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:42,660
Are you really so anxious?

303
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:49,220
Father, what's wrong?

304
00:18:54,820 --> 00:18:57,860
Xiaojiu, you've grown up.

305
00:18:58,570 --> 00:19:00,380
You're about to become the Empress.

306
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:02,460
Father,

307
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:04,460
I'm just getting married.

308
00:19:04,820 --> 00:19:05,500
Also,

309
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:08,100
I'll often come back to visit you and mother.

310
00:19:08,460 --> 00:19:09,300
Moreover,

311
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,220
His Majesty can practice the cloud-riding trick.

312
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:12,820
We can come to Qingqiu from the Sky Kingdom

313
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:14,540
in a blink of an eye.

314
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:17,820
Father, no need to be so sad.

315
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:19,420
You are going to

316
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:22,420
become the Monarch and the Empress,

317
00:19:22,780 --> 00:19:24,100
but you're still so childish.

318
00:19:24,620 --> 00:19:26,220
Even if I'm going to become the Monarch and the Empress,

319
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,060
I'm still your daughter.

320
00:19:30,260 --> 00:19:31,100
In future,

321
00:19:31,460 --> 00:19:33,300
if His Majesty dares betray you...

322
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:36,980
Father, His Majesty really treats me well.

323
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,420
Do feel relieved.

324
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:40,220
I'll be happy.

325
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,180
She said she must see you,

326
00:19:56,420 --> 00:19:58,980
and she asked me to bring this to you.

327
00:19:59,180 --> 00:20:01,140
She said you would see her after seeing it.

328
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:44,780
Master, you've come at last.

329
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:51,140
This is left by your father.

330
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:52,580
Put it away.

331
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:00,860
My father never asked you for any favor when he was alive.

332
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:02,940
Master,

333
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:06,580
this is the place where my father died.

334
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:07,540
I...

335
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:08,820
I want to beg you

336
00:21:09,900 --> 00:21:12,100
for another chance.

337
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:16,900
Even if...

338
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:18,780
Even if I have to be a fairy maid

339
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:22,540
in your mansion for the rest of my life,

340
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,660
I'm fine with that.

341
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:28,580
Master, for my father's sake,

342
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:30,260
please have mercy on me

343
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,460
and let me stay by your side.

344
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,620
Before your father died,

345
00:21:34,940 --> 00:21:36,180
he entrusted you to my care.

346
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:37,780
However,

347
00:21:38,540 --> 00:21:40,340
I never like to take care of

348
00:21:40,540 --> 00:21:42,620
someone who fancies me.

349
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:48,300
Fine.

350
00:21:51,980 --> 00:21:55,820
Now with this scale,

351
00:21:57,260 --> 00:22:01,660
I want you to fulfill your promise to my father.

352
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:07,300
I want you to return my father's favor to me.

353
00:22:07,980 --> 00:22:09,780
I want you to divorce your wife,

354
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:14,060
appoint no Empress,

355
00:22:15,900 --> 00:22:17,980
and never get married the rest of your life.

356
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:22,820
Your father would never expect that

357
00:22:23,220 --> 00:22:26,340
you would use the promise this way.

358
00:23:08,700 --> 00:23:09,700
What time is it now?

359
00:23:10,620 --> 00:23:12,980
It'll be the auspicious moment in one hour.

360
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:17,340
Fetch the ritual scroll for me.

361
00:23:17,620 --> 00:23:18,420
I'm gonna review it again.

362
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:19,420
Yes.

363
00:23:27,820 --> 00:23:28,300
Your Highness!

364
00:23:29,340 --> 00:23:29,820
Chong Lin,

365
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:31,460
where is His Majesty?

366
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:33,220
I've no idea.

367
00:23:33,700 --> 00:23:34,900
But no need to worry.

368
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:37,980
I suppose His Majesty is delayed by something urgent.

369
00:23:40,820 --> 00:23:41,860
Pardon me for being outspoken.

370
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:44,140
If His Majesty can't get back on time today,

371
00:23:44,540 --> 00:23:45,780
we can turn today's wedding banquet into

372
00:23:45,940 --> 00:23:48,220
a normal celebration banquet.

373
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:52,220
Actually, it's OK with me,

374
00:23:52,820 --> 00:23:55,100
but my father and mother are here today.

375
00:23:55,340 --> 00:23:56,540
They've prepared for days

376
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:58,340
so as to make this banquet

377
00:23:58,540 --> 00:24:00,140
a real wedding banquet.

378
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:02,300
If His Majesty doesn't show up,

379
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,300
I'm afraid they may feel hurt.

380
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:07,940
Your Highness, when sending out invitations,

381
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:09,300
we made it clear that

382
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:10,900
this would be a delayed wedding banquet.

383
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:13,300
As to what a delayed wedding banquet would be like,

384
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:15,020
no one knows actually.

385
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:17,060
If we turn it into a normal celebration banquet

386
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:19,740
for immortals to drink wine
and get together on this happy occasion,

387
00:24:20,260 --> 00:24:21,540
it won't seem odd.

388
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:24,540
Nor will it embarrass your family from Qingqiu.

389
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:29,140
This is actually a good idea.

390
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,540
His Majesty never likes banquet occasions.

391
00:24:33,820 --> 00:24:34,980
He wouldn't show up

392
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,300
even for his own victory banquet.

393
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,700
In case he doesn't show up today,

394
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:39,660
it won't lead to any misunderstanding.

395
00:24:40,020 --> 00:24:40,580
Chong Lin,

396
00:24:40,940 --> 00:24:42,460
I really appreciate that

397
00:24:42,740 --> 00:24:43,700
you've considered these for me.

398
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:45,540
Your Highness,

399
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:48,380
His Majesty takes the wedding banquet seriously.

400
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:50,140
If he can't come back on time today,

401
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,700
he must have encountered something urgent.

402
00:24:52,420 --> 00:24:54,820
He definitely cares about you.

403
00:24:56,540 --> 00:24:57,620
I believe him.

404
00:24:59,020 --> 00:25:01,100
Your Highness, pardon me for talking big.

405
00:25:01,380 --> 00:25:02,780
His Majesty asked me to prepare for this banquet

406
00:25:03,020 --> 00:25:03,860
because he trusted me.

407
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:05,460
No matter what happens,

408
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:07,420
I'll protect you.

409
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,100
Chong Lin, thank you.

410
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:11,420
Go and get things ready.

411
00:25:11,860 --> 00:25:12,620
Yes.

412
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:10,100
How lively!

413
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:13,820
I suppose the banquet has started.

414
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:16,060
Your Majesty,

415
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:18,740
where are you?

416
00:26:20,900 --> 00:26:21,660
Jiu'er!

417
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:26,540
Mother!

418
00:26:26,580 --> 00:26:27,700
Be honest with me.

419
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:29,580
Today is the big day.

420
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:30,980
Why isn't His Majesty here?

421
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:31,740
Mother,

422
00:26:32,700 --> 00:26:34,500
His Majesty is delayed by something.

423
00:26:35,300 --> 00:26:37,660
Maybe something urgent has happened.

424
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:40,660
Mother, don't worry.

425
00:26:41,060 --> 00:26:43,100
Has he told you where he has gone

426
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,380
and for what?

427
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:46,900
For fear that I might get worried,

428
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:48,140
His Majesty surely wouldn't tell me

429
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:50,220
these troublesome things.

430
00:26:50,940 --> 00:26:51,780
But mother, look!

431
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:53,860
His Majesty trusts Chong Lin the most.

432
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:55,500
He has taken care of

433
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:57,900
the following matters.

434
00:26:58,300 --> 00:27:01,060
He must have received orders from His Majesty.

435
00:27:01,380 --> 00:27:04,100
Mother, no need to worry.

436
00:27:05,340 --> 00:27:05,980
But, Jiu'er...

437
00:27:06,260 --> 00:27:07,020
Mother,

438
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:10,660
His Majesty is just late.

439
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:11,980
Moreover,

440
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:13,820
this is a delayed wedding banquet.

441
00:27:14,220 --> 00:27:15,780
I'm already the Empress of His Majesty.

442
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:18,420
I don't care about these formalities.

443
00:27:24,970 --> 00:27:26,860
I didn't expect Xiaojiu to act so quickly.

444
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:28,340
It's a pity that

445
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:30,660
I can't drink at her wedding banquet in person.

446
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:33,300
When it's all over,

447
00:27:33,660 --> 00:27:35,060
you can be a good friend

448
00:27:35,340 --> 00:27:36,700
and give her a delayed gift.

449
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,380
Then she'll have a drink with you.

450
00:27:39,460 --> 00:27:40,700
A small gathering between friends

451
00:27:41,420 --> 00:27:43,140
is far better than today's banquet, right?

452
00:27:44,940 --> 00:27:45,700
Right.

453
00:27:45,900 --> 00:27:47,220
Then I'll pick up Ji Heng.

454
00:27:47,460 --> 00:27:48,380
Wherever she wants to go later,

455
00:27:48,380 --> 00:27:49,340
I'll go with her.

456
00:27:49,860 --> 00:27:50,580
What about you?

457
00:27:51,100 --> 00:27:52,340
After all these annoyances are over,

458
00:27:52,500 --> 00:27:53,420
what will you do?

459
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:57,060
After we get rid of Miao Luo,

460
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:58,620
I still have to handle Nie Chuyin.

461
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:02,100
The rifts between different races need to be mended.

462
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:04,420
Each race needs a demon lord.

463
00:28:04,780 --> 00:28:06,220
I want to revitalize our clan,

464
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:07,500
- so I have to pick out more suitable... - So troublesome!

465
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:08,980
In my opinion,

466
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:12,140
just kill those traitors directly.

467
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:13,420
Why do you waste time

468
00:28:13,580 --> 00:28:14,540
talking to them?

469
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:19,740
Yan,

470
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:22,700
as a demon lord,

471
00:28:22,940 --> 00:28:24,780
the last lesson you need to learn is that

472
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:28,820
putting away your sword is
for drawing out your sword better.

473
00:28:37,260 --> 00:28:38,740
Your Highness, Emperor Dong Hua is here.

474
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,220
Where is he now?

475
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:41,260
At the gate of our clan.

476
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:43,540
Princess Ji Heng is also with him.

477
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:45,100
Ji Heng is back?

478
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:46,220
Let's go!

479
00:28:47,220 --> 00:28:47,940
You Majesty!

480
00:28:49,980 --> 00:28:50,500
You Majesty!

481
00:28:50,940 --> 00:28:52,700
Emperor Dong Hua is at the camp gate of our clan.

482
00:29:01,820 --> 00:29:02,700
Heng'er!

483
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:04,020
Heng'er!

484
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:06,220
Ji Heng,

485
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:08,300
how come the Qiushui Cold Toxin is more severe?

486
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:11,940
I hate people pestering me endlessly

487
00:29:12,140 --> 00:29:13,420
and threatening me with their lives the most.

488
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:16,260
You're acting so obnoxiously simply

489
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:19,260
because of your father's dragon scale.

490
00:29:22,980 --> 00:29:24,380
Though I've made a promise,

491
00:29:24,860 --> 00:29:27,540
the contents of the promise are for me to decide.

492
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,340
I'll save your life,

493
00:29:29,740 --> 00:29:31,380
remove your toxin,

494
00:29:31,620 --> 00:29:33,580
and find you a place within the territory of the demons,

495
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:37,180
thus paying back your father's favor back then.

496
00:29:38,020 --> 00:29:40,460
From now on, the dragon scale will be gone.

497
00:29:41,340 --> 00:29:44,420
In future, whether you're alive or dead,
it'll have nothing to do with me.

498
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:46,820
I don't want to see you ever again.

499
00:29:49,460 --> 00:29:51,100
Xu Yang, the Demon Lord Chi, I've got an order for you.

500
00:29:52,420 --> 00:29:53,220
Your Majesty!

501
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:58,340
I command you to withdraw your former order

502
00:29:58,500 --> 00:30:00,620
and order Demon Princess Ji Heng to return to your land

503
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:04,340
and never leave this place in future.

504
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:05,780
Any objection?

505
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:07,100
Your Majesty,

506
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:09,300
what on earth has Ji Heng done

507
00:30:09,340 --> 00:30:09,940
to make you so...

508
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:11,380
Any objection?

509
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:22,700
No, of course.

510
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,660
Heng'er!

511
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:32,700
Ji Heng!

512
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:33,980
Come on.

513
00:30:35,380 --> 00:30:35,940
Let's go.

514
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:38,300
Xiaojiu,

515
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:41,860
how come His Majesty didn't show up

516
00:30:41,860 --> 00:30:42,700
at the end of the wedding banquet?

517
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:45,180
What on earth is going on?

518
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:50,180
His Majesty is delayed by something urgent.

519
00:30:50,500 --> 00:30:51,660
What's so urgent to make him

520
00:30:51,940 --> 00:30:54,180
miss his own wedding banquet?

521
00:30:55,220 --> 00:30:56,100
Father,

522
00:30:56,460 --> 00:30:58,980
His Majesty really had something urgent to deal with.

523
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:01,220
What about this?

524
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:03,300
Mother and father, you should go back to Qingqiu first.

525
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:05,020
When His Majesty returns

526
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:05,780
after handling his business properly,

527
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:07,660
I'll take him to Qingqiu

528
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:09,980
and apologize to the elders.

529
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,620
So the so-called urgent business

530
00:31:20,500 --> 00:31:22,700
is to leave you behind at the wedding banquet

531
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:26,020
while messing around with Ji Heng from the demon clan?

532
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:28,060
Ji Heng?

533
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:32,300
Right!

534
00:31:33,100 --> 00:31:35,460
I know about Ji Heng.

535
00:31:35,740 --> 00:31:37,180
Ji Heng was poisoned with Qiushui Cold Toxin

536
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:39,700
and has relied on His Majesty
to remove her toxin ever since.

537
00:31:39,980 --> 00:31:41,300
His Majesty made a promise

538
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:42,540
to her father,

539
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:44,220
so he has pitied her all the time

540
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:45,420
and helped her.

541
00:31:45,820 --> 00:31:46,700
Pity?

542
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:49,140
How come I heard that

543
00:31:49,660 --> 00:31:51,180
this morning, he carried Ji Heng

544
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:54,020
out of the Baishui Mountain majestically

545
00:31:54,300 --> 00:31:55,860
and went directly to the demon clan?

546
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:58,340
I heard that at that time,

547
00:31:58,540 --> 00:32:00,300
the Princess clung to him delicately.

548
00:32:00,900 --> 00:32:03,380
It's really hard to tell whether he did that out of pity.

549
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:05,980
A man and a woman

550
00:32:06,460 --> 00:32:09,220
stayed at Baishui Mountain last night with no one around.

551
00:32:09,420 --> 00:32:11,100
Do you also know that?

552
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:13,020
Luckily,

553
00:32:13,620 --> 00:32:15,420
now that the demon clan is in a state of siege,

554
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:17,460
it's hard to pass information to both sides.

555
00:32:18,060 --> 00:32:19,460
I suppose only your husband

556
00:32:20,020 --> 00:32:22,700
can make that happen.

557
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:27,020
So only a few know about this.

558
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:29,580
Otherwise, if immortals from Eight Deserts know about this,

559
00:32:30,140 --> 00:32:33,860
how embarrassed our family will be!

560
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:43,380
Actually, it's not so important if we're embarrassed.

561
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:47,700
I just can't tolerate that

562
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:52,020
Dong Hua actually betrayed you!

563
00:32:55,820 --> 00:32:58,180
Father! Mother!

564
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:01,100
I want to hear him explain.

565
00:33:02,060 --> 00:33:02,900
Xiaojiu...

566
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:09,300
Why not go back to Qingqiu with us first?

567
00:33:09,940 --> 00:33:11,260
If Dong Hua really loves you,

568
00:33:11,540 --> 00:33:13,420
he'll definitely come to Qingqiu to look for you.

569
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,020
Your Highness!

570
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:25,860
Chong Lin, tell me.

571
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:27,900
If His Majesty wants to explain to me after coming back,

572
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:29,780
will two days be enough?

573
00:33:33,300 --> 00:33:34,940
Considering that His Majesty has made no mistake

574
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:36,940
as the Emperor of the Three Realms,

575
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:39,180
please don't take Her Highness away.

576
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:41,020
His Majesty is sure to come back!

577
00:33:44,340 --> 00:33:44,900
Chong Lin,

578
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:48,020
accompany me to the demon land.

579
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:49,900
I want to ask him in person.

580
00:33:50,980 --> 00:33:51,660
Yes.

581
00:34:41,700 --> 00:34:42,420
Heng'er!

582
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:44,740
Your Majesty!

583
00:34:47,140 --> 00:34:49,820
Your Majesty, something's wrong with the blood tear.

584
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:54,060
Please help us demons!

585
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,660
I'll go and investigate myself.

586
00:34:56,580 --> 00:34:57,420
Yan!

587
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:00,660
Heng'er!

588
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:02,180
Heng'er!

589
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:05,300
Please go to Bihai Cangling

590
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:07,300
and explain to Xiaobai in person.

591
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,340
After I handle the blood tear,

592
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:11,380
I'll go back to Bihai Cangling for her.

593
00:35:12,100 --> 00:35:13,420
Do ask her to wait for me.

594
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:17,660
No need to mention everything here to her

595
00:35:17,940 --> 00:35:19,300
in case she gets worried.

596
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:20,420
OK.

597
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:35,540
Ji Heng, come on.

598
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:37,380
Xu Yang.

599
00:35:37,380 --> 00:35:38,060
Yan,

600
00:35:38,700 --> 00:35:40,260
I've got a secret hiding place.

601
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:43,020
Take Heng'er there and help her settle down.

602
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:45,380
After we get rid of Miao Luo,

603
00:35:46,140 --> 00:35:47,500
we can take her back.

604
00:35:49,300 --> 00:35:50,380
Elder brother!

605
00:35:52,020 --> 00:35:53,300
You're my only sister.

606
00:35:54,220 --> 00:35:55,940
If anything happens to the demons,

607
00:35:56,620 --> 00:35:58,020
I have to leave an heiress

608
00:35:58,020 --> 00:35:59,940
for our race.

609
00:36:01,820 --> 00:36:02,340
Yan,

610
00:36:03,100 --> 00:36:04,780
take care of Heng'er for me.

611
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:07,100
OK. I'll be right back.

612
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:08,860
I'll send Ji Heng to that safe place first

613
00:36:09,180 --> 00:36:10,940
and then I'll send the message
to Bihai Cangling for His Majesty.

614
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:11,900
It'll only take half a day.

615
00:36:12,340 --> 00:36:14,380
Stay right beside His Majesty.

616
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:15,500
I see.

617
00:36:19,820 --> 00:36:20,540
Be careful!

618
00:36:21,940 --> 00:36:22,580
Elder brother!

619
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:23,260
Go!

620
00:36:26,060 --> 00:36:27,020
Demon Lord!

621
00:36:32,620 --> 00:36:33,300
Demon Lord Xu Yang,

622
00:36:33,620 --> 00:36:35,340
is His Majesty here now?

623
00:36:35,740 --> 00:36:36,420
Indeed he is.

624
00:36:37,020 --> 00:36:37,660
His Majesty...

625
00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:41,060
Is he with Ji Heng?

626
00:36:42,820 --> 00:36:45,860
His Majesty has taken Ji Heng back to our clan.

627
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,020
Now he has gone to the Forbidden Land

628
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:50,140
to check the blood tear ward.

629
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,220
Chong Lin.

630
00:36:52,860 --> 00:36:54,620
I won't stay here for long.

631
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:57,620
Since His Majesty has already been here,

632
00:36:58,500 --> 00:36:59,700
tell him when you see him that

633
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:01,340
I'll wait for him in Qingqiu.

634
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,100
Your Highness!

635
00:37:07,980 --> 00:37:09,700
Emperor Dong Hua is here.

636
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:12,460
If you're up to something,

637
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:14,860
you'd better stop.

638
00:37:15,180 --> 00:37:19,300
Incompetent as you are, how can you be a demon lord?

639
00:37:19,700 --> 00:37:22,420
The demons are really declining.

640
00:38:16,540 --> 00:38:17,300
Your Majesty,

641
00:38:17,740 --> 00:38:19,380
Demon Lord Xu Yang was killed brutally.

642
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:22,140
The Miaoyi Chasm!

643
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:38,260
Slow down.

644
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:47,100
I've checked around.

645
00:38:47,500 --> 00:38:48,860
Xu Yang has protected this place well.

646
00:38:49,220 --> 00:38:50,140
Stay right here.

647
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:51,220
Wait for me to pick you up.

648
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:52,780
Except Xu Yang or me, don't trust

649
00:38:53,060 --> 00:38:54,100
anyone who comes to pick you up.

650
00:38:56,340 --> 00:38:57,580
Leave me alone.

651
00:38:58,700 --> 00:38:59,700
Yan,

652
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,940
why are you so good to me?

653
00:39:03,700 --> 00:39:06,220
Haven't you seen what I had done for His Majesty

654
00:39:07,900 --> 00:39:09,980
and how he treated me?

655
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,060
The ice face is not the lucky guy.

656
00:39:12,380 --> 00:39:13,380
He doesn't deserve you.

657
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:15,580
I care about you. It has nothing to do with that.

658
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:23,980
I actually knelt down

659
00:39:25,100 --> 00:39:29,060
and used my late father to threaten him.

660
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:33,020
I humbled myself to the dust

661
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:36,620
and became someone I hate.

662
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:41,300
Why?

663
00:39:42,420 --> 00:39:45,260
How come I've become such a woman?

664
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:46,900
How come I've become

665
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:49,060
someone I hate?

666
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:54,340
Now I'm the disgrace of the demons.

667
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:55,020
Ji Heng,

668
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:56,380
look at me!

669
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,740
I've loved you for so long

670
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:00,740
and pursued you for so long.

671
00:40:01,140 --> 00:40:02,460
Do you find me

672
00:40:02,460 --> 00:40:04,300
a humiliating and cowardly demon lord?

673
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,140
You're not!

674
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:09,260
Right.

675
00:40:09,820 --> 00:40:11,700
You like him and want to be with him,

676
00:40:12,100 --> 00:40:13,460
so you've tried everything to get him.

677
00:40:13,460 --> 00:40:14,460
What's wrong with that?

678
00:40:15,900 --> 00:40:17,340
Yan,

679
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,500
I don't deserve your care.

680
00:40:20,780 --> 00:40:22,860
It's for me to decide whether you deserve it or not.

681
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:26,660
Ji Heng,

682
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:28,740
I've got something important to attend to.

683
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:30,180
As to what I'm gonna say next,

684
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:32,420
you can take your time and think about it while you're here.

685
00:40:33,900 --> 00:40:35,340
I don't care what you and the ice face were

686
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:37,460
and what you will be.

687
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:39,100
I only care about you.

688
00:40:39,540 --> 00:40:40,700
If you're upset,

689
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:42,620
I might as well destroy the Sky Kingdom.

690
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:47,100
I've only loved you in my entire life.

691
00:40:47,540 --> 00:40:48,980
Whenever you turn round,

692
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:50,860
I'm here.

693
00:40:54,300 --> 00:40:56,500
Even if I remain obsessive,

694
00:40:57,140 --> 00:40:58,940
will you still wait for me?

695
00:40:59,540 --> 00:41:01,020
I've waited for you for tens of thousands of years.

696
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:02,140
Compared to me,

697
00:41:02,380 --> 00:41:04,180
your tiny bit of obsession is nothing.

698
00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:07,780
Do you still remember

699
00:41:08,060 --> 00:41:08,740
the poem you liked to chant

700
00:41:08,860 --> 00:41:10,780
under the moon the most?

701
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:14,220
Green, green the reed,

702
00:41:14,620 --> 00:41:16,180
dew and frost gleam.

703
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:18,460
Where's she I need?

704
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:20,340
Beyond the stream.

705
00:41:22,020 --> 00:41:23,980
Upstream I go,

706
00:41:24,700 --> 00:41:26,460
The way is long.

707
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:28,900
Downstream I go,

708
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:32,620
she's there among.

709
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:34,660
Tell me.

710
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:39,380
Will someone also go upstream for me

711
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:42,100
despite the changes of heaven and earth

712
00:41:42,580 --> 00:41:44,540
or the evanescence of worldly affairs?

713
00:41:47,260 --> 00:41:48,380
Where's she I need?

714
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:51,260
Beyond the stream.

715
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:56,780
You failed to get an answer

716
00:41:56,980 --> 00:41:58,020
from Min Su back then,

717
00:41:58,500 --> 00:41:59,420
but now I'll answer you.

718
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:01,340
Yes.

719
00:42:01,860 --> 00:42:02,980
I did it.

720
00:42:04,940 --> 00:42:05,940
The road to follow you

721
00:42:06,220 --> 00:42:07,860
is indeed perilous and endless,

722
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:10,060
but every time I felt frustrated,

723
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:12,020
I would remember how you smiled at me

724
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,220
when we first met.

725
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:16,500
I will definitely protect you

726
00:42:17,140 --> 00:42:18,860
so that you can smile like that all the time.

727
00:42:25,980 --> 00:42:27,460
This place is very safe.

728
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:30,820
Xu Yang really cares about you.

729
00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:33,100
Feel relieved to heal your wounds here.

730
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:34,740
When it's all over,

731
00:42:36,540 --> 00:42:37,580
I'll see you again.

732
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:40,940
Yan,

733
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:46,900
this time, the demons, my elder brother and you,

734
00:42:46,900 --> 00:42:47,380
will you all...

735
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:48,220
Don't worry!

736
00:42:50,140 --> 00:42:51,100
Your elder brother and I will be here.

737
00:42:51,380 --> 00:42:52,380
Everything's gonna be all right.

738
00:42:54,580 --> 00:42:55,260
Thank you.

739
00:42:56,180 --> 00:42:57,260
For what?

740
00:42:57,580 --> 00:42:59,380
I said when we first met that

741
00:42:59,620 --> 00:43:01,380
I would die to protect Demon Lord Xu Yang

742
00:43:01,540 --> 00:43:03,020
and Princess Ji Heng.

743
00:43:04,580 --> 00:43:05,460
You'll be fine.

744
00:43:05,820 --> 00:43:06,740
So are the demons.

745
00:43:07,620 --> 00:43:08,860
Feel relieved and wait for me to return.

746
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:11,620
Yan,

747
00:43:12,940 --> 00:43:13,860
promise me

748
00:43:15,420 --> 00:43:17,140
to return safely, OK?

749
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:27,780
I'll wait for you to return!

